---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 218
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Death=The Art of Dying
  - 480
By: Sri Ramana Maharshi
---
Everyone is aware of the eternal Self. He sees so many dying but still
believes himself eternal. Because it is the Truth. Unwillingly the
natural Truth asserts itself. The man is deluded by the intermingling
of the conscious Self with the insentient body. This delusion must
end.
